title: The Fugitive S02E17 The End Is But The Beginning DivX
description:
The Fugitive
S02E17
The End Is But the Beginning
First aired: 1/12/1965

Kimble (David Janssen) takes advantage of a deadly car accident as a way to try and convince Gerard (Barry Morse) that he is now dead.

Writer: George Fass, Arthur Weiss, George Fass
Director: Walter Grauman
Guest stars: Richard Anderson (Leonard Taft), Paul Birch (Capt. Carpenter) , Barbara Barrie (Aimee), Andrew Duggan (Harlan)

Be sure to leave your THANKS in a comment if you are interested in seeing the rest of season 2.
